						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Kēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Vishuvu, Chaitra śu. 15.</hi></p>						

						<p>The record is written very indifferently. It gives a number of fanciful epithets of goddess Durga. It also mentions Ghaṇḍikōṭa Vōrugaṇṭi Pratāparudra and the fifty six countries.</p>						

						</summary>
